  "title": "Junior Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Title : Junior Engineer Project support</p><p>Job Description & Requirements : </p><p>We invite highly motivated individuals to join our team in providing support to our clients’ biomanufacturing facilities. In this role, you will be tasked with performing junior engineer role for ongoing project at Client facility and ensuring strict adherence to pharmaceutical GMP and regulatory standards.<br /></p><ul><li>Vendor qualification document controller</li><li>Migrating vendor document to Client's approved format/portal</li><li>Archival of Documentation</li><li>Hands on experience on AutoCAD, Microsoft Office, PDF, shareportal, etc. Fresh graduates are welcome to apply.</li><li>Able to edit/update AutoCAD drawings</li><li>Ensure that all project activities comply with Singapore regulatory standards, EHS policies, and Client's quality assurance protocols. </li></ul>",
